<p>Hon. Speaker, pursuant to the provisions of Standing Order 44 (2) (c) , I rise to request for a Statement from the Chairperson of the Departmental Committee on Administration and Internal Security regarding the abduction of a resident in Hulugho Sub-County, Garissa County.</p>
