            <div id="chunk-711040" class="chunk-wrapper"><div class="contributor-name"><a href="/mps-performance/national-assembly/13th-parliament/kaguchia-john-philip/">Hon. Kaguchia John (Mukurweini, UDA)</a></div><div class="speech-content"><p>Hon. Deputy Speaker, it is against this background that I seek a statement from the Chairperson of the Departmental Committee on Education on the following:</p></div></div>
          
