<p>Let me appreciate Members for settling down fast and enabling the House to embark on transaction of business of the House in earnest. Indeed, in just one week, the House has already concluded the Second Reading of five Bills. It is scheduled to vote on the Second Reading of the sixth Bill. We already did that earlier this afternoon.</p>
