<p>I challenge the Committee, because I can see the Chair and the Vice-Chair are in an animated discussion. You need to ask whoever signed and published the order to come out and account for that unconstitutional edict. To be honest, we cannot allow that level of impunity to prevail unpunished. That is unacceptable in the modern day.</p>
